reviews.review_text: Terrific This is a terrific Aud of a great show. Well worth downloading. I have a fondness for the early 80s shows - it was around that time that I first began getting my hands on tapes of shows. I was in college and had met some great people who, it seemed, were always going on tour or just back from a tour and always had great acid and new tapes to listen to, they were beautiful people, we spent countless hours in dorm rooms tripping, listening to Live Dead, and giving each other kundalini massages. OM AH HUM!

Awesome show! This show is amazing for the scarlet/fire alone!! Best ever? Perhaps. The rest of the show is absolutely smoking as well. LOTS of energy. Jerry sounds possessed! This show deserves some recognition.

What a show! I read a post once that made a good point, you must look past the quality of the recording and hear the music. This is a great example of that.  I've heard better recordings but this show is magical! The mix of the crowd and the band is enticing and draws you in even furthur...
